, Saitama|Saitama]], [[Japan]] || {{fb|Japan}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 2\u20130 || [[Exhibition game#International football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 20. || 9 September 2003 || [[Estadio Ol\u00edmpico (Caracas)|Estadio Ol\u00edmpico]], [[Caracas]], [[Venezuela]] || {{fb|Venezuela}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 3\u20130 || rowspan=\"4\"|[[2006 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|2006 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 21. || 15 November 2003 || [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Bolivia}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 3\u20130\n|-\n| 22. || 19 November 2003 || [[Estadio Metropolitano Roberto Mel\u00e9ndez|Estadio Metropolitano]], [[Barranquilla]], [[Colombia]] || {{fb|Colombia}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 1\u20131\n|-\n| 23. || 30 March 2004 || [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Ecuador}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 1\u20130\n|-\n| 24. || rowspan=\"2\"|9 February 2005 || rowspan=\"2\"| [[Merkur Spiel-Arena|LTU-Arena]], [[D\u00fcsseldorf]], [[Germany]] || rowspan=\"2\"|{{fb|Germany}} || '''1'''\u20131 \u2021 || rowspan=\"2\"|2\u20132<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dfb.de/die-mannschaft/spiele-termine/?spieledb_path=%2Fmatches%2F434638|title=SPIELE & TERMINE: Deutschland 2\u20132 Argentinien|publisher=DFB|date=9 February 2005|accessdate=14 August 2018}}</ref> || rowspan=\"2\"| [[Exhibition game#International football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 25. || '''2'''\u20132 \n|-\n| 26. || 30 March 2005 || rowspan=\"3\"| [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Colombia}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 1\u20130 || rowspan=\"3\"|[[2006 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|2006 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 27. || rowspan=\"2\"|8 June 2005 || rowspan=\"2\"|{{fb|Brazil}} || '''1'''\u20130 || rowspan=\"2\"|3\u20131\n|-\n| 28. || '''3'''\u20130\n|-\n| 29. || 12 November 2005 || [[Stade de Gen\u00e8ve]], [[Geneva]], [[Switzerland]]