 Argentina |publisher=Soccerway |date=28 February 2001| accessdate=14 August 2018}}</ref> || [[Exhibition game#International football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 13. || 28 March 2001 || [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Venezuela}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 5\u20130 || rowspan=\"5\"|[[2002 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|2002 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 14. || rowspan=\"2\"|28 April 2001 || rowspan=\"2\"| [[Estadio Hernando Siles]], [[La Paz]], [[Bolivia]] || rowspan=\"2\"|{{fb|Bolivia}} || '''1'''\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\"|3\u20133 \n|-\n| 15. || '''2'''\u20133\n|-\n| 16. || 3 June 2001 || [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Colombia}} || '''3'''\u20130 || 3\u20130\n|-\n| 17. || 15 August 2001 || [[Estadio Ol\u00edmpico Atahualpa]], [[Quito]], [[Ecuador]] || {{fb|Ecuador}} || '''2'''\u20130 \u2021|| 2\u20130\n|-\n| 18. || 12 June 2002 || [[Hitomebore Stadium Miyagi]], [[Rifu, Miyagi]], [[Japan]] || {{fb|Sweden}} || '''1'''\u20131 || 1\u20131 || [[2002 FIFA World Cup Group F#Sweden vs Argentina|2002 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n| 19. || 20 November 2002 || [[Saitama Stadium 2002|Saitama Stadium]], [[Saitama, Saitama|Saitama]], [[Japan]] || {{fb|Japan}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 2\u20130 || [[Exhibition game#International football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 20. || 9 September 2003 || [[Estadio Ol\u00edmpico (Caracas)|Estadio Ol\u00edmpico]], [[Caracas]], [[Venezuela]] || {{fb|Venezuela}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 3\u20130 || rowspan=\"4\"|[[2006 FIFA World Cup qualification (CONMEBOL)|2006 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 21. || 15 November 2003 || [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|El Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]] || {{fb|Bolivia}} || '''2'''\u20130 || 3\u20130\n|-\n| 22. || 19 November 2003 || [[Estadio Metropolitano Roberto Mel\u00e9ndez|Estadio Metropolitano]], [[Barranquilla]], [[Colombia]] || {{fb|Colombia}} || '''1'''\u